  • Method Details

    • onCallback

      void onCallback(String name, String email, String phone, String profileImage)
      Called when the Firestore query for user data is completed.

      This method provides the user details obtained from Firestore, including the user's name, email, phone, and profile image URL.

      Parameters:
      name - The name of the user, retrieved from Firestore or provided as a default.
      email - The email address of the user, retrieved from Firestore or provided as a default.
      phone - The phone number of the user, retrieved from Firestore or provided as a default.
      profileImage - The URL of the user's profile image, retrieved from Firestore or provided as a default.
